  "texts": [
    "Systematic review formIn the planning phase of the study, a review protocol is created based on the research questions determined.",
    "The goal of this protocol is to ease the review process of the researchers who participated in this study.",
    "Thus, they can reach rapidly consolidated findings during the analysis of the results.",
    "The review form consists of six sections.",
    "The sub-items determined in the form are adapted from previous review studies and are described in detail as follows.1."
  ]
}